### ✅ **Updated Project Structure for Full Vlog Forge Feature Set**

Here’s the **scalable project structure** with the current progress marked.

```
VlogForge/
├── main.py                  # Entry point of the app
├── core/ # in progress...
│   ├── content_manager.py   # Handles content scheduling, auto-updates, and reminders # ✅ Done
│   ├── engagement_tracker.py # Engagement tracking, audience insights, and heatmaps # ✅ Done
│   ├── auto_posting.py      # Auto-posting scheduler for optimal timing # ✅ Done
│   ├── ai_caption_suggester.py # AI-based title and caption generation # ✅ Done
│   ├── batch_content_generator.py # Generate multiple vlog scripts at once # ✅ Done
│   ├── referral_tracker.py  # Tracks referrals for user acquisition # In Progress
│   ├── lead_magnet.py       # Automates resource distribution and conversion tracking # ✅ Done
│   ├── a_b_testing.py       # A/B testing logic for content optimization # In Progress
│   ├── hashtag_performance.py # Tracks hashtag effectiveness across platforms # In Progress
│   ├── audience_tracker.py  # Tracks top engaged users & super fans # In Progress
│   ├── engagement_heatmap.py # Analyzes best posting times & trends # In Progress
│   └── pdf_report_generator.py # Creates weekly/monthly performance reports # In Progress
├── ui/
│   ├── main_window.py       # Main dashboard layout with tabbed interface # In Progress
│   ├── script_generator.py  # Vlog script generation module # In Progress
│   ├── content_calendar.py  # Content planning, scheduling, and automation # In Progress
│   ├── engagement_tracker.py # Engagement analytics and growth tracking # In Progress
│   ├── reflection_prompts.py # Journal-based reflection prompts for vlog ideas # In Progress
│   ├── idea_vault.py        # Store spontaneous vlog and content ideas # In Progress
│   ├── auto_highlight.py    # Extract key quotes from vlogs for tweet-sized content # In Progress
│   └── social_engagement_bot.py # Optional: Automate Twitter likes/comments # In Progress
├── data/
│   ├── engagement_data.csv  # Stores historical engagement metrics
│   ├── content_schedule.csv # Tracks vlog scheduling and statuses
│   ├── hashtag_analysis.csv # Stores hashtag performance data
│   ├── follower_growth.csv  # Tracks user acquisition and growth trends # ✅ Done
│   ├── referral_data.csv    # Stores referral program details
│   └── lead_magnet_data.csv # Tracks user conversions from free resources
├── assets/
│   ├── icons/               # App icons and UI assets
│   ├── styles.qss           # Custom UI styling
│   ├── templates/           # Email templates for lead magnet automation
│   └── pdf_reports/         # Auto-generated weekly/monthly reports
├── api_integrations/
│   ├── twitter_api.py       # Twitter API integration for posting & engagement tracking
│   ├── youtube_api.py       # YouTube API integration for video tracking
│   ├── mailchimp_api.py     # Handles lead magnet automation
│   ├── google_calendar.py   # Optional: Sync content schedule with Google Calendar
│   ├── firebase_db.py       # Optional: Cloud storage for multi-device sync
│   └── web_scraper.py       # Scrapes data from relevant sites (e.g., trending stock posts)
└── README.md                # Project documentation
```

---

### **Key Features & Where They Fit**

| Feature                         | Module(s)                                   | Status      |
|---------------------------------|--------------------------------------------|-------------|
| **Auto-Post Scheduler**         | `auto_posting.py`                          | ✅ Done     |
| **Batch Content Generator**     | `batch_content_generator.py`               | ✅ Done     |
| **AI-Driven Title & Caption Suggestions** | `ai_caption_suggester.py`            | ✅ Done     |
| **Engagement Heatmap**          | `engagement_heatmap.py`                    | In Progress |
| **Audience Interaction Tracker**| `audience_tracker.py`                      | In Progress |
| **Hashtag Performance Tracker** | `hashtag_performance.py`                   | In Progress |
| **Content Idea Vault**          | `idea_vault.py`                            | In Progress |
| **Auto-Highlight Generator**    | `auto_highlight.py`                        | In Progress |
| **Daily Reflection Prompts**    | `reflection_prompts.py`                    | In Progress |
| **Weekly/Monthly Reports**      | `pdf_report_generator.py`                  | In Progress |
| **A/B Post Testing**            | `a_b_testing.py`                           | In Progress |
| **Follower Growth Tracker**     | `follower_growth.csv`, `engagement_tracker.py` | ✅ Done  |
| **Referral Program Tracker**    | `referral_tracker.py`                      | In Progress |
| **Lead Magnet Automation**      | `lead_magnet.py`                           | ✅ Done    |
| **Social Engagement Bot (Optional)** | `social_engagement_bot.py`             | In Progress |

